ts will have to enter the OTP sent on the registered mobile no. in the Bihar Corona Tatkaal Sahayata Mobile app. The amount of CM Vishesh Sahayata Yojana would be transferred into the bank accounts of the applicants through Direct Benefit Transfer (DBT) mode.\u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0935\u093f\u0936\u0947\u0937 \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u0902\u0924\u0930\u094d\u0917\u0924 \u092c\u093f\u0939\u093e\u0930 \u0938\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0939\u0930 \u0932\u0949\u0915\u0921\u093e\u0909\u0928 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092b\u0902\u0938\u0947 1,03,579 \u0932\u094b\u0917\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0916\u093e\u0924\u0947 \u092e\u0947\u0902 10,35,79,000 \u0930\u09420 \u0930\u093e\u0936\u093f \u0905\u0902\u0924\u0930\u093f\u0924 \u0915\u0940 \u0917\u0908\u0964 https://t.co/omtJMWsfTd pic.twitter.com/AuojedHZsb\u2014 Nitish Kumar (@NitishKumar) April 7, 2020 Bihar CM Vishesh Sahayata Yojana Implementation & ProgressBihar CM Nitish Kumar on 6 April 2020 launched Mukhyamantri Vishesh Sahayata Yojana by clicking mouse of computer at CM Residence in Patna.Implementation Within minutes of clicking of mouse by CM, an amount of Rs. 1,000 per migrant worker was transferred in bank accounts of total 1,03,579 workers through DBT mode. Accordingly, a total sum of Rs. 10,35,79,000 was transferred on 6th April.Progress Till date, over 3.10 lakh migrant workers had applied for Rs. 1,000 assistance either through link on disaster management website or Corona Tatkal Sahayata App. In just 3 days after uploading of link on 3rd April on website / app, around 3.10 lakh migrant labourers applied online and applications are still pouring on dept\u2019s website.A maximum of 55,264 applications comes from Delhi state followed by 41,050 from Haryana, 30,576 from Maharashtra and 25,638 from Gujarat. Minimum 8 applications were received from Lakshadweep union territory. Out of total 1.03 lakh workers who received assistance, max. 7281 are originally from Saran district followed by 6,821 from Muzzafarpur and 6,792 from Madhubani. Minimum 469 beneficiaries belong to Arwal district.References\u2014 To get complete information on Bihar govt. initiatives to Tackle Coronavirus, read press release of Disaster Mgmt. Dept. published on 6 April 2020 through the link \u2013 http://disastermgmt.bih.nic.in/notice/COVID-19_06.pdf \u2014 Also visit the official website of Bihar Disaster Management at disastermgmt.bih.nic.in \u2014 Check the direct link to apply online \u2013 aapda.bih.nic.in \u2014 For any technical assistance on app, send and e-mail to cmrf.sadm@gmail.com and you can contact to the following helpline numbers: Krishna \u2013 8789410978 (M), Abhinav \u2013 7667426822 (M), Raj \u2013 9534547098 (M), Adarsh \u2013 8292825106 (M), Inderjit \u2013 8986294256 (M), Shubham \u2013 8271226204 (M).  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/nitish-kumar-transfers-rs-10-35-cr-in-bank-ac-of-1-03-lakh-workers-from-bihar/articleshow/75015602.cms  at  "}